OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,FITV News Central filmed students
OL,7,Flearning life saving skills in the
OL,8,Fevent of a stabbing, as Journalist
OL,9,FAlice Smith reports
OL,11,FSchoolchildren as young as 11 years
OL,12,Fold are being taught how to treat stab
OL,13,Fwounds and manage bleeding.
OL,15,FCitizenAID, a charity which trains
OL,16,Fpeople to respond in an emergency and
OL,17,Frun the sessions, said high-profile
OL,18,Fcases of youth violence have led to an
OL,19,Fincrease in demand for them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
