OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,FThe idea for these lessons came from a
OL,7,Fstudent at Light Hall School in
OL,8,FSolihull following a stabbing.
OL,10,FThe charity was co-founded by
OL,11,FProfessor Sir Keith Porter who is a
OL,12,Fformer Consultant Trauma Surgeon at
OL,13,Fthe Queen Elizabeth Hospital.
OL,15,F"Stabbing is quite prevalent in the UK
OL,16,Fat the moment," he said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,F"People are dying unnecessarily, and
OL,7,Fwhat we want to do is train a mass of
OL,8,Findividuals who know how to stop the
OL,9,Fbleed, just using simple first-aid
OL,10,Fdrills."
OL,12,FAnd it was one of the students
OL,13,Fthemselves who came up with the idea
OL,14,Ffor the sessions to be taught in
OL,15,Fschool after becoming concerned about
OL,16,Fserious knife violence in the area.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,F"I just think, especially in secondary
OL,7,Fschools, a lot of the students don't
OL,8,Fhave enough understanding of (how to
OL,9,Ftreat stab wounds)," said Amelia
OL,10,FBrain, a year nine pupil here.
OL,12,F"I just think that if we're more aware
OL,13,Fof it, then it will be easier to
OL,14,Fapproach it."
OL,16,FIt comes not long after the murder of
OL,17,F12-year-old Leo Ross, who was stabbed
OL,18,Fin January last year while walking
OL,19,Fhome from his school just a few miles
OL,20,Faway.
OL,26,@pD@^pmqD@Rpn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,FIt had a profound affect, not just on
OL,7,Fhis school mates, but on the wider
OL,8,Fcommunity too.
OL,10,F"When you see the news you hear about
OL,11,Fhow prominent it is and how common it
OL,12,Factually is around where we are and
OL,13,Ffor people our age," said one of the
OL,14,Fyear nine girls, Miriam, who was
OL,15,Fparticipating in the session.
OL,17,FHer classmate, Riley, agreed: "It's
OL,18,Fjust good to know how to treat knife
OL,19,Fwounds, if you ever do get stabbed. It
OL,20,Fis a scary thing, though."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,FWhile another girl, Ava, said you
OL,7,Fnever know when the skills might prove
OL,8,Fvital, saying: "You always think it's
OL,9,Fnever going to happen to you but it
OL,10,Fjust could at any point."
OL,12,F"It could be you or someone you know;
OL,13,Fyour family, your friends, your
OL,14,Fneighbour."
OL,16,FBut while the students were grateful
OL,17,Fto be taught these life saving skills,
OL,18,FI asked their pastoral manager,
OL,19,FKhadijar, Mohammed, whether it is
OL,20,Fconcerning they are having to be
OL,21,Ftaught at all.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,F"Of course it's concerning," she said.
OL,8,FYoung kids are getting targeted and
OL,9,Fyou don't know (about it). As parents,
OL,10,Fas carers, as an older sister myself,
OL,11,Fit's really heartbreaking to see.
OL,13,F"But I think it's great to raise
OL,14,Fawareness and that's what we're about:
OL,15,Fraising awareness."
OL,17,FA new part of the curriculum?
OL,26,@qD@PpmqD@Ypn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,FBut more than just raising awareness,
OL,7,Fthe Conservative MP for Solihull West
OL,8,Fand Shirley, Dr Neil Shastri-Hurst,
OL,9,Fwants to go a step further by making
OL,10,Fthese sessions a compulsory part of
OL,11,Fevery child's education: "I would like
OL,12,Fto see, as part of our national
OL,13,Fcurriculum, life-saving skills being
OL,14,Fdelivered.
OL,16,FBefore adding, "That's not just about
OL,17,FCPR, but stop the bleed training, too,
OL,18,Fto ensure people are prepared. That if
OL,19,Fthere is an emergency, they know how
OL,20,Fto act and that they can act calmly in
OL,21,Forder to save lives."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775070658
OL,3,C'It's heartbreaking to see': Students
OL,4,Ctaught stab survival skills at school
OL,6,FAlthough there are clearly significant
OL,7,Fconcerns around serious youth violence
OL,8,Fand knife crime, the Government told
OL,9,FITV News Central that nearly 60,000
OL,10,Fknives had already been taken off
OL,11,FBritain's streets, and knife homicides
OL,12,Fhad fallen by 28%.
OL,14,FWhile these students in Solihull are
OL,15,Flearning a stark lesson, it's one that
OL,16,Fcould see teenagers like them save a
OL,17,Flife.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
